My bicycle runs a Teensy++ board powered by a lead-acid battery.
A number of LEDs are wired to the board and taped to parts of
the bicycle.

Position        LEDs         Teensy PIN

On-Board       Orange        D6
Teensy

Handlebar      White         B3
Headlamp

Forks          Blue          D1

Handlebar      Blue          D2
Ends

Back           Ultraviolet   D4

Back left      Red           B5(bad)
               Green         B6
               Blue          B7

Back right     Red           C6
               Green         C7
               Blue          D7

Bucket         Green         B4
Underneath
